  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the investigators study is to demonstrate in healthy subjects and a cohort of
      patients infected with HIV, the presence of miRNAs in circulating peripheral blood
      microparticles (MPs).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
